Mod3 k :Exec /usr/local/bin/run-or-raise Firefox firefox
Mod3 j :Exec /usr/local/bin/run-or-raise urxvt urxvt

Mod4 space :RootMenu

Mod4 w :Close
Mod4 q :kill

Mod4 k :Minimize
Mod4 H :ShowDesktop

Mod4 m :WindowMenu

